UltraJSON is a fast and extendable JSON encoder and decoder written in pure C

Python bindings are available as the module ujson with the methods decode and encode

Preliminary benchmarks:

Python 2.6.6 (r266:84297, Aug 24 2010, 18:46:32) [MSC v.1500 32 bit (Intel)]
OS Version: 6.1.7601 Service Pack 1 Build 7601
System Type: x64-based PC
Processor: Intel(R) Core(TM)2 Quad CPU Q9550 @ 2.83GHz 2.83 GHz
Total Physical Memory: 8191 MB

Medium complex object:
ujson encode      : 9701.76398 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 2533.28459 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 2033.84520 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 7099.84076 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 3576.44118 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 3560.42455 calls/sec

Array with 256 strings:
ujson encode      : 23475.66583 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 15761.71144 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 6380.28810 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 24244.54916 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 16521.64853 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 21222.01344 calls/sec

Array with 256 doubles:
ujson encode      : 26901.16704 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 2053.22667 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 2137.50788 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 28402.75917 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 4106.88699 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 4406.45790 calls/sec

Array with 256 True values:
ujson encode      : 100027.29321 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 34573.37598 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 47241.69040 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 98493.55648 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 58052.86797 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 75066.85997 calls/sec

Array with 256 dict{string, int} pairs:
ujson encode      : 11224.13126 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 3824.41512 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 3074.12671 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 12567.90822 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 7967.31714 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 7071.16988 calls/sec

Dict with 256 arrays with 256 dict{string, int} pairs:
ujson encode      : 38.35051 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 11.80735 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 12.96582 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 35.33706 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 25.33494 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 21.69531 calls/sec

See (python/benchmark.py) for further information.

NOTE: These benchmarks are preliminary! 

